Description
===========
Redhare is a command-like tool to capture the result table
from the Hong Kong Jockey Club website.
http://racing.hkjc.com/racing/Info/meeting/Results/english/Local/


Installation
============
First set up the virtualenv
$ pipenv install

Then run the setup.py
$ python setup.py develop

Usage
=====
Usage: redhare [OPTIONS]
A command tool to capture the result table from Hong Kong Jockey Club

Options:
--date TEXT      Date of match. Format:YYYYMMDD
--venue [ST|HV]  Venue: ST or HV
--table TEXT
--help           Show this message and exit.

Example
=======
$redhare --date='20170910' --venue='ST'